<div class="title">On Top of the World... For Awhile</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamine (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=geesh&Exact=1">geesh</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; geesh. "On Top of the World... For Awhile: An Experience with Amphetamine (Adderall) (exp9409)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 13, 2001. erowid.org/exp/9409</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

